00:03:00.010 --> 00:03:03.280
And you can also get
notified if Nearby is enabled

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:05.170
or disabled for your app.

00:03:05.170 --> 00:03:08.570
So great new features for you
to use with the Nearby Messaging

00:03:08.570 --> 00:03:09.430
